{"tid":2335563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被揭人臉識別系統　可辨識維吾爾人　阿里巴巴：已刪除種族標記功","createTime":"2020-12-22T03:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T04:14:16.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e99fe5d8981a3e70aa0202eadd03f78a749eac6a","tid":2335563,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/被揭人臉識別系統-可辨識維吾爾人-阿里巴巴-已刪除種族標記功能/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%A8%E8%AD%98%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%BE%E7%88%BE%E4%BA%BA-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4-%E5%B7%B2%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%A8%99%E8%A8%98%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%2F&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=0ccea538\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%89%E8%AD%98%E5%88%A5%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E5%8F%AF%E8%BE%A8%E8%AD%98%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%BE%E7%88%BE%E4%BA%BA-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4-%E5%B7%B2%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E6%A8%99%E8%A8%98%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%2F&h=653f8acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/被揭人臉識別系統-可辨識維吾爾人-阿里巴巴-已刪除種族標記功能/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國科技龍頭之一阿里巴巴研發的人臉辨識系統，日前被揭發可用作辨識新疆維吾爾族人，惹來外界質疑；阿里巴巴今日發表聲明，指阿里巴巴將不再容許其產品用作針對及辨識特定族裔人士；又指對人臉識別系統包含族裔辨識功能感到「沮喪 (dismayed) 」，已將所有產品內的種族標記功能刪去。<br />\n<br />\n人工智能科技雖為生活上帶來不少便利，但也有機會被濫用甚至侵害人權。影象監控研究組織 IPVM 日前從阿里巴巴網站，發現網頁介紹對人臉識別系統的介紹中，示範了可用於辨識維族人或其他小數族裔的功能，同時附有相關使用詳細說明。根據網站簡介，用戶可以簡單地將圖片或影片上傳，系統則可判斷圖中或片中人，是否維族人。不過相關資料在 IPVM 查詢後，已被阿里巴巴刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D5xvK1VqjkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD5xvK1VqjkM&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2Fa0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=0120f461\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D5xvK1VqjkM</a><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴在未有提供進一步證據及原因下解釋，這些功能「只可在測試環境中使用」。路透社引述該公司今日發表的聲明指，阿里巴巴將不再容許產品，針對辨識特定族裔人士；指公司對於包含族裔辨識功能感到「沮喪 (dismayed) 」，亦已將所有產品種族標記功能刪去。<br />\n<br />\nIPVM 從系統兩份說明書發現，兩份都寫有系統可判斷輸入的資料中，是否包含「少數族裔」或者「少數族裔（維族人）」的字眼。<br />\n<br />\nIPVM 亦發現另一間中國雲端服務企業 Kingsoft，也疑似有辨識維族人功能，但隨後也刪除了該功能，並指從未銷售相關功能。此外，IPVM 上周也聯同《華爾街日報》揭發，華為系統也可用作辨識維族人，球星基沙文也因此宣佈終止與華為合作。<br />\n<br />\n新疆維吾爾族人權狀況惡劣，較早前已有不少媒體報道，當地不少維族人被以「再教育」為名，關押在當地的「再教育營」，部份人被迫強制勞役，部份產品亦出口至全球各地。美國較早前就指此些涉事產品涉違人權，禁止入口銷售。"},{"pid":"8537af476dd19ab0533bf6f38635bc8e5b948e44","tid":2335563,"uid":268591,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"痴線 邊個會信"},{"pid":"9449abfe56fcff686b156a304052f5bad898ab50","tid":2335563,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"已刪除近平即時觀看功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a23e99609eb8dbe75460ce4ae50e957c199b67","tid":2335563,"uid":103363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"即係隨時加得番"},{"pid":"1566f801d4fc0e26484c39d34f0cbd37330cdc7d","tid":2335563,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:04:48.000Z","msg":"公安嗰到一定有㗎啦 互惠互利"},{"pid":"113f13af31c1632a0639fbfc56b5b6a457838e2d","tid":2335563,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"種族標記功能刪去 唔代表冇其他標記喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新加個叫疑似恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3290a2210f9865e2f659a6ef2abc223169dec7c0","tid":2335563,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bceaf2ff8804cfe445245f5b5dfbc7ff9e93cc","tid":2335563,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"點樣係minority又唔係asian<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a9b8192096dade36cb7068c85a55fa323da61d","tid":2335563,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:14:16.000Z","msg":"啫係承認有做過呢個功能<br />\n係咪真delete 又另一回事"}]}